Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.45,0:00:08.53,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林家的推理龍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.13,0:00:12.19,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}推理？ 感覺跟平時風格不太一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.55,0:00:14.24,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}這個特典也進行到第六集了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:16.11,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}要防止千篇一律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:18.45,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}所以說不要說這種高次發言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.65,0:00:19.89,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}這樣也不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:21.65,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}怎麽了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:24.19,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}不 只是在想你會不會又要脫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:27.26,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}不要啦 同樣的梗玩兩次就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:28.83,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}真是這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:31.09,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}那這也來試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.81,0:00:33.73,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.41,0:00:36.91,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林家的兩小時懸疑龍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:43.28,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}露科亞大人 你就是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.54,0:00:44.78,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}真是荒謬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.96,0:00:47.56,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}說我就是犯人 有什麽證據嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:50.04,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}確實有這樣的場景呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:52.83,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}殺人現場的監控器已經把你拍下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.97,0:00:55.36,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}已經把你裸奔逃走的畫面拍下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:00:57.06,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}完 完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:00:58.01,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}才剛說完那種話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.01,0:00:59.37,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}這不是馬上就脫了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.90,0:01:02.31,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林家的封閉空間龍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.22,0:01:05.72,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}您 您難道就是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:10.76,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}解决了好幾起無頭案件的女高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:13.11,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}名偵探 小林托爾大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.49,0:01:15.06,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}是的 比起這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.07,0:01:18.40,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}在還沒有發現那個連續無差別殺人犯之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.79,0:01:20.34,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}今天還是大家一起睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.73,0:01:21.54,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.77,0:01:24.14,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}畢竟不知道犯人藏在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.23,0:01:25.67,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}行動必須要慎重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:28.57,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}喂 犯人找到了 就在那
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.37,0:01:31.65,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林家的密室手法龍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.43,0:01:35.59,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}犯人用鈍器之類的東西殺害了露科亞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.08,0:01:37.22,maidragon-screen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55\c&H3324A7&\frz40.88\pos(392,701.999)}好想脫衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.93,0:01:37.53,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}不過 這個房間是密室
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.84,0:01:38.87,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}密室
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.25,0:01:40.87,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}真的是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:42.94,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}像這樣使用魔法陣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:45.03,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}其實很簡單就可以自由出入了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:46.99,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}只有你可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:49.84,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林家的時刻表詭計龍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.56,0:01:54.83,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}托爾大人 果然在這車上的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:56.86,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}根本沒有作案時間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.04,0:01:58.67,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}等一下 難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:03.87,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}這樣的話 就可以充分趕上犯罪的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:06.19,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}所以說只有你可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.74,0:02:08.89,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林家的恐嚇信龍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:12.28,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}沒想到翔太居然會被綁架
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.04,0:02:15.61,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}托爾大人 犯人寄來的恐嚇信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.91,0:02:16.61,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:17.68,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}你逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:19.69,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}不管你在哪裏 我都在注視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:21.28,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}我會奪走你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.39,0:02:23.63,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}總有一天 你的心會變成屬￿我的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:25.90,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}你最好覺悟吧 小林
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:29.30,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}這是我昨天寫的情書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.80,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}因爲沒有貼郵票所以被退回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:33.86,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}那張情書 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:36.40,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}小林家的福爾摩斯龍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:40.01,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}是委托人吧 請進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:41.75,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:43.83,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}雖然這麽說很突然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:45.86,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}但是你是正在洗澡中途急忙趕過來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:47.62,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}你是怎麽知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:50.16,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}那還沒完全幹透的頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:51.96,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}流著汗的肌膚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:53.76,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}而且比起這些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:55.17,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}這具什麽都沒穿的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.68,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}已經如實反映了事實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.10,0:03:00.05,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}是是 全裸全裸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:01.22,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}你隨意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:02.32,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:07.31,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}我早就知道 肯定會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:08.75,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}那麽下一集是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:10.38,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}終于到了最後一集了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:12.02,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:14.30,maidragon-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}終于要結束了啊
